CONCLUSION
================================================================================

NeuroAssist demonstrates that effective cognitive monitoring doesn't require 
expensive equipment, complex ML models, or invasive sensors. By combining 
evidence-based clinical assessments with thoughtful UX design and intelligent 
rule-based analytics, the platform provides meaningful early detection 
capabilities while maintaining patient dignity and caregiver peace of mind.

The system is production-ready for pilot deployments and can be extended with 
additional features as needed. Its modular architecture and clear separation 
of concerns make it maintainable and scalable.

Built with accessibility, clinical validity, and user experience at the core, 
NeuroAssist offers a practical solution for the growing need for cognitive 
health monitoring in aging populations.


